Following the postponement of the 2020 event due to the coronavirus pandemic,
the 2021 London Landmarks Half Marathon is scheduled for 23 May 2021. Find out
You’ll be required to complete a further short registration form and pay a
non-refundable registration fee. You will also be required to raise a minimum
sponsorship of £375 within the 4 weeks following the event date.
**Throughout January, you can sign up for just £1**
## Our Team Goodies for everyone to enjoy
* Dedicated fundraising and training support, including a fundraising pack and regular updates including Facebook Lives.
* Your own personalised Diabetes UK technical running vest.
* Free 'Crazy Hair' and 'Bang bang sticks'.
* Lots of support from our Cheer Squad along the route and post race including massage.
* Exclusive access to our Facebook group and Strava group for you and your fellow team members.
We would love to hear from you and answer any question you may have. Contact
our Fundraising events team on 0345 123 2399 or
